       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    ARI30108.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA ARI30108.                                         *
      *                                                                *
      *     Aplicaçăo Inactivas
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *             20181106                                           *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE ARI30108         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAD0500 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY ARCV3010.
       COPY ARCV3011.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0010.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY ARCK0001.
       COPY ARCK0002.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-VIAT0500                 PIC X(08) VALUE 'VIAT0500'.
           05 WS-PROGNAME                  PIC X(08) VALUE 'ARI30108'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE ARI30108         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO ARCV3010-MSG
                                              ARCV3011-MSG.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2200-ELIMINA-DADOS
                 THRU 2299-ELIMINA-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF.

       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2200-ELIMINA-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2200-ELIMINA-DADOS.

           INITIALIZE DCLVIAD0500.

           MOVE ARCV3010-APLIC             TO VIAD0500-APLIC
           MOVE ARCV3010-SERVCODE          TO VIAD0500-SERVCODE

           EXEC SQL
              DELETE FROM VIAT0500_INACTIV
               WHERE APLIC    = :VIAD0500-APLIC
                 AND SERVCODE = :VIAD0500-SERVCODE
           END-EXEC

           MOVE CON-VIAT0500               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

           EVALUATE TRUE
              WHEN DB2-OK
                 CONTINUE
              WHEN DB2-NOTFND
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                                           TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE ARCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                                           TO ARCV3011-SERVCODE-S
                 MOVE ARCK0001-REGISTO-N-EXISTE
                                           TO ARCV3011-SERVCODE-MSG
              WHEN OTHER
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ABEND-DB2   TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE VIAK0001-ERRO-DB2    TO VIAL0002-COD-ERRO-GRAVE
           END-EVALUATE.

       2299-ELIMINA-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.

           MOVE ARCV3011-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE ARCV3011-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE ARCV3011-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES                     TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0010.
